Field Detail

broadcastEvents

public static boolean broadcastEvents
Flag to turn on or off SDK event broadcasting. When receiving a broadcast the following extras could be in the intent. "packageName" - String - string of the originating package to filter out broadcasts from other apps running the Millennial Media SDK. "error" - Serializable - an MMException object for error events. "startedIntent" - Int - the type of intent started for ACTION_INTENT_STARTED events. "id" - Int - the id of the MMAdView if applicable. 0 by default.
